@startuml System_Architecture
!theme plain
title System Architecture

node "Client Side" {
    [Browser] as Client
}

node "Docker Host" {
    node "Web Container" {
        [Django Web Server] as Django
        [Business Logic & AI] as Logic
    }
    
    node "Database Container" {
        database "PostgreSQL" as DB
    }
}

Client --> Django : HTTP/HTTPS
Django --> DB : SQL Queries
Logic --> DB : Read/Write Training Data

@enduml
